edu.ncsu.csc216.tracker.ticket

Class TrackedTicket

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.tracker.ticket.TrackedTicket

  • public class TrackedTicket
extends java.lang.Object
    TrackedTicket is a class which maintains all of the history of the progression of the TrackedTicket through the Finite State Machine. The object is constructed with parameters title, submitter, and note. The submitter is the noteAuthor of the first Note in the TrackedTicket.
    Author:
    Scott Spencer
